  "title": "Turbo Manifold compatible with Honda Civic Acura Integra B16 B18 SCHEDULE40 T3 44mm WG FE605310",
  "handle": "fe605310-turbo-manifold-compatible-with-honda-civic-acura-integra-b16-b18-schedule40-t3-44mm-wg",
  "description": "<h4>Application</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>1990-2001 Acura Integra with 1.6L/1.8L B16/B18 DOHC VTEC</li>\n  <li>1999-2000 Honda Civic Si/EX-R SIR Coupe with 1.6L/1.8L B16/B18 DOHC VTEC</li>\n  <li>1994-1997 Honda Civic del Sol VTEC Coupe with 1.6L/1.8L B16/B18 DOHC VTEC</li>\n  <li>For B16/B18 DOHC VTEC motors only</li>\n  <li>NOT compatible with stock A/C and P/S</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Features</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Fits T3 or T3/T4 hybrid turbo</li>\n  <li>Excellent quality and durability to improve vehicle performance</li>\n  <li>Tubular manifold design with better exhaust flow and delivers more top end power</li>\n  <li>Equal length runners for balanced exhaust reversion and enhanced turbo performance</li>\n  <li>Precision aligned tubes made of schedule 40 cast 304 stainless steel</li>\n  <li>Head flanges laser-cut from high quality 1/2-inch thick steel plates</li>\n  <li>The flange is flattened by a hydraulic press for precise and leak free sealing</li>\n  <li>All joints are golden color TIG brass style welded to prevent cracking and wear</li>\n  <li>Flanges chrome plated for corrosion resistance</li>\n  <li>Sandblasted surface for extra hardness</li>\n  <li>The accessories in the photos are included</li>\n  <li>1 year warranty for any manufacturing defect</li>\n  <li>No instructions provided; professional install recommended</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>Technical Specifications</h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<strong>Manifold Type:</strong> Tubular Turbo Manifold</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Runner Diameter:</strong> 1-3/4 in. (45mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Runner Layout:</strong> Equal Length</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Turbo Fitment:</strong> T3, T3/T4 Hybrid</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Turbo Mount Position:</strong> Low/Bottom Mount</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Wastegate Fitment:</strong> 44mm (V-band)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Head Flange Thickness:</strong> 1/2 in. (13.5mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Pipe Thickness:</strong> Schedule 40 (3mm)</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Material:</strong> 304 Stainless Steel</li>\n  <li>\n<strong>Finish:</strong> Sandblasted</li>\n</ul>\n",
